sentences.english: The current-loop is a key subsystem of the magnetic levitation controller on maglev vehicle.
sentences.chinese: 電流環是磁浮列車懸浮控制器的重要子系統。

sentences.english: The terminal of the train is BAGOU.
sentences.chinese: 本次列車終點站是巴溝站。

sentences.english: Hastily fled on The journey of the train.
sentences.chinese: 便匆匆逃上了遠行的列車。

sentences.english: During the depression, I used to hop freights at least once a month.
sentences.chinese: 大蕭條時期，我一月至少一次要偷偷搭乘貨運列車。

sentences.english: Is there any dinning car on the train?
sentences.chinese: 請問這列車上有咐餐廳嗎？

sentences.english: "Xi Nan Jiao"is a transfer station. You may transfer subway line 2.
sentences.chinese: “西南角”是換乘車站，您可以換乘地鐵2號線列車。

sentences.english: Next station is Wangjing, please get ready for your arrival.
sentences.chinese: 列車運行前方，是望京站，下車乘客請提前做好準備。

sentences.english: The railway timetable shows the time when the trains arrive and depart.
sentences.chinese: 列車時刻表告訴人們火車到站和開車的時間。

sentences.english: The train will be ready to leave when all the carriages have been coupled.
sentences.chinese: 在所有車廂都連接好時列車即可開出。

sentences.english: The magnetic-levitation train ride from the international airport to the city is the perfect metaphor for Shanghai.
sentences.chinese: 從國際機場到市區的磁懸浮列車線是上海的最佳名片。

sentences.english: The teminal station is Xinzhuang. Next stop is People's square.
sentences.chinese: 本次列車開往莘莊，下一站人民廣場。

sentences.english: I stayed with OSV as long as I was painting trains basically.
sentences.chinese: 我住的OSV只要我基本上是繪畫列車。

sentences.english: We have arrived in Tsuen Wan, please exit from the train, thank you.
sentences.chinese: 本班列車已經抵達荃灣站，請所有乘客落車，多謝。

sentences.english: We may ride the magnetic suspension train to go to the Pudong international airport.
sentences.chinese: 我們可以乘磁懸浮列車去浦東國際機場。

sentences.english: Body-fitted hexahedron grid was obtained of high speed train head surface based on mapping approach.
sentences.chinese: 利用映射法生成高速列車頭部流場的六面體貼體網格。

sentences.english: Express trains don't stop at Princeton junction.
sentences.chinese: 特快列車不在普林斯頓樞紐站停車。
